summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 5440 for the improvement of 17th Avenue Southwest, from Iowa Avenue to a point about 300 feet south of the south margin of West Andover Street; by constructing watermains and otherwise improving the same, under Ordinance No. 68505, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
